	Forum Upgrade ~ Forums ~ 08-17-2003</td></tr>
	<tr><td class=border>Finally found the time to upgrade all forums to SP 1.3.1.
<br><br>
I don't have the time to hack out all the admin settings I don't want you forum admins playing with, so you get some fun new features to toy with (including Avatars). Don't screw me over on this. I'll yank these forums faster than you can eat a stack of orroes with a cold glass of milk. Be careful what you change in there. You could cripple your entire forum. If you have any questions, view the help manual <a href="http://forums.guildtools.net/YaBBHelp/">HERE</a>.
<br><br>
Also, you'll be able to modify the template and change the look of your forum if you wish. Do not remove the guildtools.net links. That's a quick way to get your forum removed.
<br><br>
If you have any problems with the new upgrade please let me know.
<br><br>
I'll be adding more Avatars at a later date for you to play with.</td></tr></table><br><br>
