Note: News may be replaced by me with updates from the Guildtools Network periodically.</td></tr></table><br><br>
		<table width=80% cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td class=title>
	Forum Hosting Available ~ Forums ~ 03-23-2003</td></tr>
	<tr><td class=border>I'm happy to announce forum hosting again for the first time in a long time. Forums are YaBB Gold 1.2 which I think you'll find are very slick. <br>When you sign up for a forum you become the admin - gaining complete control over categories, layout, users, privacy and a few more goodies.<br><br>
Forums are limited to guild use for online games. Any deviation will result in board removal. Forum creation is instant, provided you supply the correct email address.</td></tr></table><br><br>
	
